r%20rentals.%20It%20also%20touts%204X%20points%20on%20flights%20and%20hotels%20purchased%20directly%20with%20the%20airline%20or%20hotel%2C%20up%20from%203X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20points%20system%20for%20the%20card%20is%20somewhat%20complicated%20(part%20of%20why%20I%20have%20always%20avoided%20a%20points-based%20card)%2C%20and%20people's%20individual%20situations%20will%20vary%20a%20lot%20about%20whether%20this%20card%20is%20better%20or%20worse%20or%20worth%20it.%20For%20some%20people%2C%20the%20higher%20yearly%20fee%20will%20net%20out%20with%20all%20the%20new%20rewards%3B%20for%20others%2C%20they're%20thinking%20of%20downgrading%20to%20a%20cheaper%20version%20or%20canceling%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20all%20of%20the%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Reserve%20cardholders%20the%20best%20journey%20to%20the%20path%20that%20works%20best%20for%20them.%20Me%2C%20I'm%20just%20feeling%20a%20huge%20burden%20lifted%20off%20my%20shoulders.%20Ahhhh%20%E2%80%A6.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchase-sapphire-reserve-credit-cards-new-fee-why-i-hate-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750801045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685b01fd85e81483682cb06a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchase-sapphire-reserve-credit-cards-new-fee-why-i-hate-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chase's%20Sapphire%20Reserve%20credit%20card%20became%20a%20millennial%20touchstone.%20I%20never%20got%20one%20when%20it%20first%20came%20out%20%E2%80%94%20and%20felt%20FOMO.%20Now%20I'm%20vindicated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchase-sapphire-reserve-credit-cards-new-fee-why-i-hate-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Ho