0positive%20for%20the%20stock%20that%20has%20largely%20been%20seen%20as%20an%20AI%20laggard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhoward-marks-memo-perplexity-ai-warren-buffett-tech-investing-wildfires-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPerplexity%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20search%20engine%20that%20responds%20to%20queries%20with%20cited%20responses%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20a%20Google%20search%20that%20returns%20links.%20If%20completed%2C%20the%20acquisition%20would%20provide%20Apple%20with%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20AI%20offering%20instead%20of%20building%20one%20out%20in-house%20over%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20an%20outright%20acquisition%2C%20could%20also%20help%20Apple%20to%20a%20lesser%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20such%20deal%20(we%20do%20not%20have%20any%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20probability%20of%20such%20a%20deal)%20would%20likely%20be%20positive%20for%20shares%20that%20are%20currently%20in%20the%20penalty%20box%20given%20Apple%20is%20largely%20viewed%20as%20an%20AI%20laggard%20(deep%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsiri-apple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESiri%3C%2Fa%3E%20integration%20delayed%20and%20no%20cutting%20edge%20models)%2C%26quot%3B%20Wamsi%20Mohan%2C%20technology%20research%20analyst%20at%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20acquisition%20would%20give%20Apple%20access%20to%20Perplexity's%20search%20and%20answering%20capabilities%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-talent-wars-recruiting-hiring-white-hot-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efresh%20AI%20talent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20product%20synergies%20with%20Siri%20and%20other%20Apple%20offering%2C%20and%20exposure%20to%20non-Google%20search%2C%20Mohan%20highlighted.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20Perplexity%20could%20revitalize%20Siri's%20capabilities%2C%20which%20have%20struggled%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20developments%20in%20chatbots.%20Perplexity%20could%20also%20be%20integrated%20with%20not%20just%20Safari%20but%20also%20system-wide%2C%20helping%20Apple%20build%20AI%20into%20its%20services%20and%20hardware.%20All%20of%20these%20factors%20could%20fetch%20a%20higher%20valuation%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Faapl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20an%20acquisition%20would%20provide%20Apple%20with%20a%20clear%20AI%20strategy%20and%20prevent%20Perplexity%20from%20being%20acquired%20by%20a%20competitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224c8979b-01f3-4902-8b35-bed3d7df6f6e%5C%22%3EAcquisition%20risks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompetition%20in%20the%20AI%20space%20is%20fierce%2C%20and%20Apple%20certainly%20isn't%20alone%20in%20pursuing%20a%20potential%20M%26amp%3BA%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-scale-ai-15-billion-alexandr-wang-acquihire-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eacquihire%3C%2Fa%3E%20strategy.%20As%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20scramble%20to%20grab%20market%20share%20in%20the%20rapidly%20developing%20AI%20industry%2C%20growing%20through%20inorganic%20means%20is%20becoming%20more%20common.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-competition-whatsapp-chatbot-battleground-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20invested%20%2414.3%20billion%20into%20data%20annotation%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-xai-openai-pull-back-meta-scale-ai-investment-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EScale%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20also%20tried%20to%20acquire%20Perplexity%20and%20another%20AI%20startup%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-who-revolted-against-sam-altman-just-started-research-lab-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESafe%20Superintelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20not%20to%20say%20that%20locking%20down%20a%20hot%20AI%20startup%20like%20Perplexity%20would%20solve%20all%20of%20Apple's%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntegrating%20a%20young%20startup%20into%20a%20larger%2C%20more-established%20company%20comes%20with%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20organizational%20challenges%2C%20and%20Mohan%20pointed%20to%20some%20of%20Apple's%20previous%20M%26amp%3BA%20ventures%2C%20such%20as%20Siri%20or%20Laserlike%2C%20as%20examples%20of%20acquisitions%20that%20experienced%20delays%20or%20roadblocks.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20will%20need%20to%20customize%20parts%20of%20Perplexity's%20platform%20to%20fit%20into%20its%20existing%20ecosystem%20and%20scale%20up%20to%20Apple's%20much%20larger%20user%20base.%20There%20are%20also%20legal%20risks%3A%20Perplexity%20is%20facing%20a%20copyright%20infringement%20case%2C%20which%20Apple%20would%20need%20to%20take%20on%20in%20the%20case%20of%20an%20acquisition.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20Perplexity%20could%20also%20jeopardize%20Apple's%20existing%20partnership%20with%20Google%2C%20creating%20a%20potential%20headwind%20to%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20these%20concerns%2C%20Mohan%20is%20cautiously%20optimistic%20on%20the%20payoff%20of%20a%20potential%20acquisition%3A%20%26quot%3BFrom%20an%20investor's%20vantage%20point%2C%20a%20deal%20would%20offer%20a%20high-reward%20but%20high-risk%20proposition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20execution%2C%20in%20our%20view%2C%20is%20paramount%3A%20Apple%20would%20need%20to%20break%20from%20some%20of%20its%20old%20habits%20(siloed%20development%2C%20extreme%20secrecy%2C%20slow%20rollout)%20to%20fully%20capitalize%20on%20Perplexity's%20fast-paced%20innovation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20completed%2C%20the%20acquisition%20would%20be%20Apple's%20biggest%20ever%2C%20as%20Perplexity%20is%20currently%20valued%20at%20%2414%20billion.%20It%20would%20also%20be%20a%20marked%20departure%20from%20the%20company's%20traditional%20free%20cash%20flow%20strategy%20of%20conducting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fapple-record-stock-buyback-bigger-boeing-airbnb-chipotle-market-cap-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estock%20buybacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20paying%20dividends.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20believes%20Apple%20could%20certainly%20afford%20to%20shell%20out%20for%20a%20deal%20of%20this%20size%2C%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-earnings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompany%20posted%20profits%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fd18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net%2FCIK-0000320193%2Fb986f1de-d226-4e8e-9304-29a8458440ec.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2424.8%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Q1%202025.%20A%20Perplexity%20deal%20would%20signal%20to%20investors%20that%20Apple%20is%20willing%20to%20shift%20its%20capital%20allocation%20strategy%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20transformative%20potential%20of%20AI%2C%20many%20analysts%20believe%20that%20not%20investing%20aggressively%20in%20AI%20is%20the%20bigger%20risk%2C%20even%20for%20a%20company%20as%20successful%20as%20Apple%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohan%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-perplexity-ai-acquisition-investor-stock-rebound-meta-google-bofa-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750796623000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685afa96f748d8c055f4483e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-perplexity-ai-acquisition-investor-stock-rebound-meta-google-bofa-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20stock%20down%2020%25%20in%202025%2C%20Apple%20could%20be%20poised%20for%20a%20comeback%20with%20a%20bold%20strategic%20mov