lans%20to%20decommission%20two%20of%20its%20Ohio-class%20SSGNs%20in%202026%20and%20the%20other%20two%20in%202028%2C%20replacing%20them%20with%20Virginia-class%20Block%20V%20submarines.%20These%20won't%20be%20dedicated%20cruise%20missile%20submarines%2C%20but%20they%20will%20boast%20greater%20firepower%20than%20earlier%20Virginias.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilitary%20leaders%20and%20experts%20have%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20replacement%20plan%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20missile%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20will%20experience%20a%20big%20drop%20in%20its%20capacity%20for%20stealthy%20missile%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said.%20The%20Block%20V%20Virginia-class%20attack%20submarines%20will%20each%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20up%20to%2040%20Tomahawk%20missiles%2C%20far%20less%20than%20the%20Ohio%20SSGNs%2C%20a%20concern%20as%20the%20US%20attempts%20to%20turn%20its%20focus%20to%20higher-end%20threats%20and%20potential%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20Navy%20officials%20will%20have%20to%20deploy%20four%20or%20more%20Virginia-class%20attack%20subs%20to%20fire%20as%20many%20long-range%20missiles%2C%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20attack%20subs%20for%20other%20missions%20they%20are%20specially%20built%20for%3A%20surveillance%20and%20ship-killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20Ohio-class%20SSGNs%20have%20two%20crews%20of%20about%20150%20sailors%20that%20rotate%20the%20sub%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20maximize%20its%20deployed%20time.%20Over%20two%20decades%20of%20operations%2C%20these%20subs%20have%20earned%20reputations%20as%20workhorses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20Block%20V%20submarines%20are%20facing%20years-long%20delays%20and%20rising%20costs%20due%20to%20persistent%20US%20Navy%20shipbuilding%20problems%20that%20could%20leave%20a%20capability%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Navy%20review%20last%20year%20estimated%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-u