20%3C%2Fem%3E(natural%20liquid%20fertiliser%20made%20from%20cow%20dung)%20to%20boost%20fruit%20size%20and%20soil%20fertility.%20Using%20natural%20fertilisers%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20your%20input%20costs%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnshul%E2%80%99s%20model%20showcases%20the%20potential%20for%20sustainable%20and%20profitable%20farming.%20He%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20taking%20risks%20in%20agriculture%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20historical%20figures%20like%20Vasco%20da%20Gama%20and%20Columbus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-16-1750735982.webp%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-16-1750735982.webp%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-16-1750735982-300x157.webp%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-16-1750735982-500x262.webp%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-16-1750735982-768x402.webp%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-16-1750735982-150x79.webp%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-454529%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnshul%20believes%20that%20taking%20risks%20is%20imperative%20to%20building%20a%20thriving%20farming%20career.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20had%20not%20ventured%20into%20the%20unknown%2C%20we%20may%20not%20have%20discovered%20the%20sea%20route%20to%20India%20and%20discovered%20America.%20My%20father%20also%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20fear%20taking%20risks%2C%20you%20will