20Frams%20%E2%80%94%20also%20a%20flavoured%20drinks%20business%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20started%20by%20Marzban%E2%80%99s%20grandfather%2C%20Framroze.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20browse%20through%20the%20current%20menu%20at%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20reveals%20a%20caffeine-free%20cola%2C%20peach%2C%20pineapple%2C%20green%20apple%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejeera%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20drink%20featuring%20cumin%20powder)%2C%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20kala%20khatta%3C%2Fem%3E%20(java%20plum%20juice)%20and%20tonic%20water.%20These%20are%20Marzban%E2%80%99s%20innovations%20%E2%80%94%20tradition%20with%20a%20wink%2C%20if%20you%20will.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20yellowing%20recipe%20and%20a%20hefty%20legacy%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%20into%20one%20of%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20Iranian%20eateries%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20spot%20a%20familiar%20silhouette.%20The%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20bottle%20is%20unmistakable.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20weighty%20legacy%20to%20carry%20forward%2C%20Marzban%20learnt%20when%20entrusted%20with%20the%20business%20in%202013%2C%20following%20the%20passing%20of%20his%20father.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20know%20anything%20at%20the%20time.%20How%20do%20I%20make%20the%20flavours%3F%20What%20do%20I%20do%3F%20And%20then%2C%20I%20came%20across%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305528%2Fcookbook-baking-food-history-books-recommended-by-madhur-jaffrey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20old%20yellow%20notebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20my%20father%20had%20scribbled%20down%20the%20formulas%20for%20the%20drink.%20I%20started%20going%20through%20his%20files%2C%20deciphering%20the%20scribbles%2C%20e