ld-fashioned%20goodness%20in%20a%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750649400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fcarbon-dioxide-1-1750417384.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D452524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20predates%20Coca-Cola%2C%20which%2C%20records%20estimate%20to%20be%20an%20invention%20of%201886%20%E2%80%94%20two%20years%20after%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20started%20in%20a%20small%20rented%20barrack%20in%20Pune.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F452524%2Fardeshirs-in-pune-was-started-by-a-zorastrian-immigrant-and-serves-flavoured-soda-drinks%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turn%20Your%20Balcony%20into%20a%20Mini%20Farm%3A%20Grow%20Jackfruit%20with%20Your%20Kids%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWant%20to%20teach%20your%20kids%20sustainability%20and%20the%20joy%20of%20homegrown%20food%3F%20Imagine%20harvesting%20a%20jackfruit%2C%20the%20largest%20fruit%20grown%20in%20India%2C%20right%20in%20your%20backyard%20or%20even%20on%20your%20balcony.%20Now%20picture%20doing%20it%20with%20your%20kids%2C%20turning%20every%20step%20into%20a%20lesson%20in%20nature%2C%20responsibility%2C%20and%20the%20magic%20of%20watching%20something%20grow%20from%20seed%20to%20harvest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESounds%20like%20an%20unattainable%20task%3F%20Not%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F301095%2Fokra-chinese-potato-moringa-how-i-grow-vegetables-around-my-house%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMini%20Sreekumar%2C%20a%20home%20gardener%20from%20Thrikkakara%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kerala%2C%20who%20has%20turned%20a%20tiny%20five-foot%20perimeter%20around%20her%20house%20into%20a%20lush%20edible%20garden